modules.description: This module implements DNS message handling over TCP and UDP protocols using MirageOS networking abstractions. It provides functions to send and receive DNS packets, including TCP flow management, buffer reading/writing, and UDP packet transmission. Concrete use cases include building DNS servers and clients that handle queries over TCP and UDP in a MirageOS unikernel.

This module implements DNS message handling over TCP and UDP using MirageOS networking abstractions. It provides functions to send and receive DNS packets, manage TCP flows, and handle buffer reading and writing for DNS messages. Use cases include building DNS servers and clients that process queries over TCP and UDP within a MirageOS unikernel.
